{"tid":637453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[cctvb]喬曉陽:港人也有權監督共產黨","createTime":"2018-04-21T19:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T03:20:32.000Z","uid":36901,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"4018383101a84b7d8f58ae7d5e897fe5462b7f8a","tid":637453,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T19:00:47.000Z","msg":"全國人大前法律委員會主任委員喬曉陽說，香港市民亦有權監督中國共產黨。 全國人大前法律委員會主任委員喬曉陽表示：「我們的人民擁護和支持中國共產黨，就是擁護和支持由一個全心全意為人民服務，而不謀求自身利益的政黨。香港雖然實行資本主義制度，但香港居民作為中華民族的一分子，這樣一個政黨值不值得支持呢？所有香港居民同全國各族人民一樣，也有權利監督中國共產黨，是不是忠實履行自己的誓言，中國共產黨也始終歡迎人民群眾的監督。」 \t\t<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5adab22ae60383570e6890ae\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5adab22ae60383570e6890ae&d=STQxmMVzxdb4Sb%2BTFhduyiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=7a5cd526\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5adab22ae60383570e6890ae</a><br />\n<br />\ncctvb你咪撚刪呢段新聞呀<br />\n<br />\n咁撚鐘意9up，你喬曉陽歪曲憲法，鼓動對香港人民實行資產階級專政，背叛共產主義，點先可以舉報呢類反革命份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076d574f61fae6d9249133311178a746c12a849d","tid":637453,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T19:04:16.000Z","msg":"監督=/=會捉晒啲狗官"},{"pid":"a3af5e08de1e808d03eeb8a403dd382b2905b23c","tid":637453,"uid":3649,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T20:59:20.000Z","msg":"我屋企聽新聞聽到呢句都冷笑咗一下"},{"pid":"fdb74482016ada4576043371d0261cd68d1d4ac6","tid":637453,"uid":34010,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T21:12:22.000Z","msg":"到時只要消滅發現問題既監督，問題就不存在"},{"pid":"3a3f4594b8a41412c6b7ef3065afd791b4b626f6","tid":637453,"uid":108022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T21:14:45.000Z","msg":"港人也有權監督強姦犯tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d122ceafb22c60382a6a0ecf26772182df810d","tid":637453,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0